metadata.name: Soaring Agoras: ROSHI!
metadata.description:
This is the Agora... called ROSHI! A floating rock vessel with a few human inhabitants. :) It is a small paradise, a refuge for those who seek peace from a turbulent world.

Each Agora is handdrawn, with final colors and renderings done in photoshop! Full res image, 300dpi. Twitter: https://twitter.com/smoothcolorator

'SOAGO19'
Art by SmoothColorator
